  "text": "For the tt example presented in this section, we use the approximate next-to-next-toleading order tt cross-section of σ tt = 894 ± 4 +73+12 −46−12 pb at a top mass of m t = 175 GeV [CITATION_1] . For the SUSY examples in the next two sections we use leading order cross-sections.",
